headline: Barbie Pink Convertible Built by Disney Up for Grabs at No Reserve Auction!
summary: The Volo Museum, world renowned for its collection of famous and one of a kind vehicles, is unlocking its vault to offer collectors a rare opportunity: a once in a lifetime chance to own the only known real Barbie car in the hands of the public.
